<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>windows - Tag | SPAWN2PWN</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/tags/windows/</link><description>Hugo FixIt 作者，喜欢瞎折腾、造轮子、写东西，分享一些前端开发中的所见、所闻、所思。</description><generator>Hugo 0.163.3 &amp; FixIt v0.4.5</generator><language>en</language><managingEditor>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</managingEditor><webMaster>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</webMaster><copyright>This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License.</copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 18:39:48 +0700</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/tags/windows/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>WAMPServer 自定义网站根目录等设置</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/wamproot/</link><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2019 18:44:36 +0800</pubDate><author>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</author><guid>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/wamproot/</guid><category domain="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/categories/memo/">Memo</category><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;使用 WAMPServer 时自定义网站根目录。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description></item><item><title>ubuntu + windows 双系统默认启动项设置</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/windefault/</link><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2019 12:48:30 +0800</pubDate><author>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</author><guid>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/windefault/</guid><category domain="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/categories/os/">OS</category><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;双系统默认启动项是 Ubuntu，而日常使用最多的还是 Windows，所以说很不方便，一不小心就开机到 Ubuntu 去了。今天来设置一下。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description></item><item><title>win10,ubuntu 双系统时间不一致</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/ubuntutime/</link><pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2019 14:28:10 +0800</pubDate><author>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</author><guid>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/ubuntutime/</guid><category domain="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/categories/os/">OS</category><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我的 Ubuntu 和 Windows 双系统是 Ubuntu 是第一启动项，所以总是开机忘记点下键，一进 Ubuntu 系统时间就不对了（总是少了 8 小时），回到 Windows 时间也是错的。知道是错的调整一下还好。忘记调了有时候真的会误事。比如说 git 版本控制提交会遇到问题种种等。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description></item><item><title>windows 上搭建 web 服务器</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/web-server-win/</link><pubDate>Fri, 26 Oct 2018 21:56:18 +0800</pubDate><author>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</author><guid>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/web-server-win/</guid><category domain="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/categories/grocery/">Grocery</category><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我用的 win10&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 class="heading-element" id="打开控制面板"&gt;&lt;span&gt;0.1 打开控制面板&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e6%89%93%e5%bc%80%e6%8e%a7%e5%88%b6%e9%9d%a2%e6%9d%bf" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;选择并进入“程序”，双击“启用或关闭 Windows 服务”，在弹出的窗口中选择“Internet Information Services”下面所有地选项，点击确定后，开始更新服务。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;a class="lightgallery" target="_blank" href="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/web-server-win/images/1.png" title="打开控制面板" data-thumbnail="/ctf-writeups/posts/web-server-win/images/1.png" data-sub-html="&lt;h2&gt;打开控制面板&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;打开控制面板&lt;/p&gt;"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" src='https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/web-server-win/images/1.png' alt="打开控制面板" height="742" width="1408"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;figcaption class="image-caption"&gt;打开控制面板&lt;/figcaption&gt;
 &lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 class="heading-element" id="查看"&gt;&lt;span&gt;0.2 查看&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e6%9f%a5%e7%9c%8b" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;更新完成后，打开浏览器，输入&lt;code&gt;http://localhost&lt;/code&gt;或者&lt;code&gt;127.0.0.1&lt;/code&gt;回车，如果此时出现 IIS7 欢迎界面，说明 Web 服务器已经搭建成功。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;a class="lightgallery" target="_blank" href="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/web-server-win/images/2.png" title="查看" data-thumbnail="/ctf-writeups/posts/web-server-win/images/2.png" data-sub-html="&lt;h2&gt;查看&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;查看&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>